Usage Instructions:
===================
To build, run make with the appropriate makefile depending on your OS/setup ('make' or 'make build')
To run, again run make but this time using the 'run' rule ('make run')

Controls:
=========
Q,E - Translate the objects
W - Cycle through the axes of translation
A,D - Rotate the objects
S - Cycle through the axes of rotation
Z,C - Scale the objects
X - Cycle through the axes of scaling

Move Left Light:
I,O - Move Left Light on X
J,K - Move Left Light on Y
N,M - Move Left Light on Z

Move Right Light (NUMPAD ONLY):
7,8 - Move Right Light on X
4,5 - Move Right Light on Y
1,2 - Move Right Light on Z
